(OOC: I was just wondering, now that Inferno's gone, are is their 
going to be a new council member?)

Starscream.

Starscream nodded at Drillbit.

"Exactly my point! But I still stand firm on what KitKat said. She 
wants to go to the Alliance. She doesn't trust these Preds. They 
worked for Hell Beast, Megatron's enemy. When she recovers she'll 
want to leave. I see no point in going when we would just leave 
again. But, it is still your decisioon Terrorsaur. And make it 
quickly. KitKat's life hangs in the balance."
